casting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/stockholm-2016|title=Stockholm 2016|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Gothenburg]]\n| [[Scandinavium]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1985|1985]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/gothenburg-1985|title=Gothenburg 1985|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Malm\u00f6]]\n| [[Malm\u00f6 Isstadion]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1992|1992]]\n| <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.svt.se/melodifestivalen/melodifestivalen-1992/|title=Melodifestivalen 1992|publisher=[[Sveriges Television]]access-date=24 November 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/malmo-1992|title=Malmo 1992|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Malm\u00f6 Arena]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2013|2013]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/malmo-2013|title=Malmo 2013|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"| 5\n|rowspan=\"4\"| {{NED}}\n| [[Hilversum]]\n| [[AVRO (broadcaster)|AVRO Studio]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1958|1958]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/hilversum-1958|title=Hilversum 1958|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Amsterdam]]\n| [[Amsterdam RAI Exhibition and Convention Centre|RAI Congrescentrum]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1970|1970]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/amsterdam-1970|title=Amsterdam 1970|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[The Hague]]\n| [[Congresgebouw|Nederlands Congresgebouw]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1976|1976]], [[Eurovision Song Contest 1980|1980]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/event/the-hague-1976|title=The Hague 1976|publisher=[[European Broadcasting Union]]|accessdat