ara International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Al Ain International Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|OMAL}}</ref>\n| [[United Arab Emirates]]\n| {{Coord|24|15|42|N|055|36|33|E|type:airport_region:AE|name=Al Ain International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Al Asad Airbase]]<ref>{{WAD|ORAA}}</ref>\n| [[Iraq]]\n| {{Coord|33|47|08|N|042|26|28|E|type:airport_region:IQ|name=Al Asad Airbase}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Antonio Maceo Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|MUCU}}</ref>\n| [[Cuba]]\n| {{Coord|19|58|11|N|075|50|07|W|type:airport_region:CU|name=Antonio Maceo Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Athens International Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|LGAV}}</ref>\n| [[Greece]]\n| {{Coord|37|56|11|N|023|56|40|E|type:airport_region:GR|name=Athens International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Basra International Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|ORMM}}</ref>\n| [[Iraq]]\n| {{Coord|30|32|56|N|047|39|43|E|type:airport_region:IQ|name=Basra International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Boryspil International Airport]]<ref name=\"EURO\"/>\n| [[Ukraine]]\n| {{Coord|50|20|41|N|030|53|36|E|type:airport_region:UA|name=Boryspil International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Chimore Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|SLCH}}</ref>\n| [[Bolivia]]\n| {{Coord|16|59|20|S|065|08|30|W|type:airport_region:BO|name=Chimore Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Ciudad Real Central Airport]]<ref name=\"EURO\"/>\n| [[Spain]]\n| {{Coord|38|51|23|N|003|58|12|W|type:airport_region:ES|name=Ciudad Real Central Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Don Miguel Hidalgo y Costilla International Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|MMGL}}</ref>\n| [[Mexico]]\n| {{Coord|20|31|18|N|103|18|40|W|type:airport_region:MX|name=Don Miguel Hidalgo y Costilla International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Donetsk International Airport]]<ref name=\"EURO\"/>\n| [[Ukraine]]\n| 