varnabhumi Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|-\n| [[Tashkent International Airport]]<ref>{{WAD|UTTT}}</ref>\n| [[Uzbekistan]]\n| {{Coord|41|15|28|N|069|16|52|E|type:airport_region:UZ|name=Tashkent International Airport}}\n| {{Convert|4000|m|disp=tablecen|0}}\n|}\n\n; Notes\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{note|A|A}} The runway also has a {{convert|9000|ft|abbr=on}} unpaved overrun on [[Rogers Dry Lake]] giving a total length of {{convert|24024|ft|abbr=on}}<ref name=\"EAFBGS\">[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/facility/edwards.htm Edwards Air Force Base] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100505185606/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/facility/edwards.htm |date=2010-05-05 }} at Globalsecurity.org</ref>\n{{refend}}\n\n==Other notable runways==\n{| border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=3 class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"font-weight:bold; background-color: #DDDDDD\"\n! Airport name\n! Country\n! Coordinates\n! Length (m)\n! Length (ft)\n|-\n| [[Edwards Air Force Base]]<ref name=\"EAFBGS\"/><sup>,</sup> {{ref|C|C}}\n| [[United States]]\n| {{coord|34|55|50|N|117|50|16|W|type:airport_region:US|name=Edwards Air Force Base, runway 17/35}}\n| 4,579\n| 15,024\n|-\n| [[White Sands Space Harbor]]<ref>[http://www.nasa.gov/centers/wstf/spaceharbor/Capabilities.html White Sands Space Harbor - Capabilities] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614181714/http://www.nasa.gov/centers/wstf/spaceharbor/Capabilities.html |date=2013-06-14 }} [[NASA]]</ref><sup>,</sup> {{ref|D|D}}\n| [[United States]]\n| {{coord|32|56|36|N|106|25|10|W|type:airport_region:US|name=White Sands Space Harbor}}\n| 10,668\n| 35,000\n|-\n| [[Edwards Air Force Base]]{{ref|C|C}}\n| [[United States]]\n| {{coord|34|56|35|N|117|51|43|W|type:airport_region:US|name=Edwards Air Force Base, runway 15/33}}\n| 8,988\n| 29,487\n|-\n| [[Nellis Air Force Base]]{{Ref|E|E}}\n| [[United States]]\n| {{coord|36|14|10|N|115|02|03|W|type:airport_region:US|name=Nellis Air Force Base}}\n| 7,341\